Display VIVA MAGENTA at home, school, or in the office with the limited edition notebook. A must-have accessory for any color enthusiast.

PANTONE® 18-1750 Viva Magenta is a brave and fearless red shade demonstrating a new signal of strength. Powerful and empowering, PANTONE 18-1750 Viva Magenta vibrates with vim and vigor, encouraging experimentation and self-expression without restraint. Audacious, full of wit, and inclusive of all, PANTONE 18-1750 Viva Magenta welcomes anyone and everyone with the same verve for life and a rebellious spirit.

